            <![CDATA[ <h2 id="toc_0">Agricultural Cooperatives</h2>
<p>In honor of <strong>World Food Week</strong> and <a href="http://goo.gl/ZJtm6">World Food Day</a> (October 16th), we learned about <strong>agricultural cooperatives</strong>.</p>

<h3 id="toc_1">Video</h3>
<p>First, we watched the following video about the work being done to
help support cooperatives in various countries.</p>

<iframe width="640" height="360" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/hmOoUgMDfLo" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>

<h3 id="toc_2">Reading</h3>
<p>Next, I divided up <a href="http://goo.gl/ooyBi">this leaflet</a> into six sections 
and had everyone read one section and take notes. Make sure to bring 
your notes and your section to class on Friday because you will be sharing
what you read with students that read other sections.</p>

